short_desc: Group focuses on providing women with skills and information needed to cope more effectively with traumatic life experiences resulting in being upset, angry, self destructive
description: Group focuses on providing women with skills and information needed to cope more effectively with traumatic life experiences resulting in being upset, angry, self destructive, having trouble concentrating, feeling out of control, broken, guilty, ashamed, having trouble trusting others, having bad things always happen or having physical like chronic pain, digestive problems, heart symptoms.
